{
	"info": {
		"name": "BCS - Update Vapi Assistant Settings",
		"description": "Updates call quality settings for all 6 BCS debt collection assistants:\n- Enable backchanneling\n- Enable background denoising\n- Increase confidence threshold (0.4 → 0.6)\n- Increase endpointing (300ms → 500ms)\n- Increase wait time (0.6s → 0.8s)\n\nThese changes improve:\n1. Interruption handling (won't talk over caller)\n2. Transcription accuracy (fewer mishears)\n3. Natural conversation flow",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
